# Code owners for required review on PRs.
#
# IMPORTANT BEFORE HANDOFF: replace the @your-org/<team> placeholders with
# the actual GitHub team handles for the operations team. PRs will fail
# their required-reviewer check until these resolve to a real team.

# Global fallback
*                       @your-org/indexing-pipeline-owners

# Deploy + CI require extra scrutiny (changes here can break production)
/scripts/               @your-org/indexing-pipeline-owners @your-org/devops
/.github/               @your-org/devops
/Jenkinsfile.deploy     @your-org/devops
/Jenkinsfile.run        @your-org/devops

# Search schema changes affect the live index
/search/                @your-org/indexing-pipeline-owners

# Function app code is the runtime path for every indexer call
/function_app/          @your-org/indexing-pipeline-owners
